SimpleProvider
=========

NotePad sample go with all SDK seem not easy for beginner because it added many stuff for NotePad features.
This example give you a simplified version.

You only need:
1 class implements your provider : SimpleProvider (with querry and insert only)
1 class contains constant you need: RememberMe
1 class for main activity, which insert and get data from your provider

Remember to check the AndroidManifest.xml!
